To ensure that the portal works correctly on different web browsers, we need to:

1. Ensure that our HTML and CSS follow best practices for cross-browser compatibility.
2. Utilize polyfills for JavaScript to handle differences in browser implementations.
3. Use responsive design principles so that the application looks and works properly across various browsers.

Epic Title: Responsive Design

We will focus on enhancing and organizing the existing templates and static resources to ensure cross-browser compatibility.

